#   Below causes a circular requirement I want to avoid completely
#   "obconf:::a graphical client to configure openbox"

with info    last 20130813
with version stable 3.5.2 3.5.0
with base    imlib2 libXcursor libXinerama libXrandr librsvg pango startup-notification
with also    --enable-static=no
with role    window-manager
with trait   x11
with source  stable http://openbox.org/dist/openbox/openbox-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    home http://openbox.org
with wmbin   /usr/bin/openbox
with info    cite 'window manager for X11
It was originally based on Blackbox and currently remains very similar,
even using Blackbox styles (with available extensions) for its themeing.'
